arh%20mayoral%20election%20declared%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%20the%20validly%20elected%20mayor%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20ruled%20that%20presiding%20officer%20Anil%20Masih%20made%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20deface%20eight%20ballots%20which%20were%20cast%20in%20favour%20of%20Kumar%20so%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20candidate%2C%20Manoj%20Sonkar%2C%20was%20declared%20the%20elected%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYesterday%2C%20the%20Presiding%20Officer%20made%20a%20solemn%20statement%20before%20this%20Court%20that%20he%20had%20done%20so%20as%20the%208%20ballots%20were%20defaced.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20none%20of%20the%20ballots%20are%20defaced%20%5Bbefore%20Masih%20made%20markings%20on%20them%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%20after%20it%20examined%20the%20defaced%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bench%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20presiding%20officer%20has%20to%20be%20deprecated%20at%20two%20levels.%20First%2C%20he%20has%20unlawfully%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20the%20mayoral%20election.%20Second%2C%20in%20making%20a%20solemn%20statement%20before%20the%20court%20on%20February%2019%2C%20the%20presiding%20officer%20expressed%20falsehood%20for%20which%20he%20must%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20above%20reasons%2C%20we%20have%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20results%20declared%20by%20the%20presiding%20officer%20are%20unlawful%20and%20have%20to%20be%20set%20aside%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20taking%20a%20stern%20action%20against%20Masih%2C%20the%20bench%20ruled%20that%20a%20fit%20case%20is%20made%20out%20for%20the%20initiation%20of%20proceedings%20under%20Section%20340%20CrPC%20(court%20monitored%20inquiry)%20against%20him.%20%E2%80%9CRegistrar%20Judicial%20is%20directed%20to%20issue%20a%20notice%20to%20Anil%20Masih%2C%20to%20show%20cause%20as%20to%20why%20steps%20should%20not%20be%20initiated%20against%20him%20under%20Section%20340%20CrPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESC%20says%20no%20to%20fresh%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solicitor%20general%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20Masih%2C%20had%20sought%20fresh%20polls%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20ideally%20wanted%20as%20it%20had%20already%20inducted%20three%20AAP%20councillors%20to%20muster%20enough%20numbers%20in%20case%20of%20re-polling.%20But%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20against%20this%2C%20as%20the%20bench%20stated%20that%20they%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20setting%20aside%20the%20entire%20election%20process%20is%20inappropriate%20as%20the%20only%20infirmity%20was%20found%20in%20the%20counting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20aside%20the%20entire%20election%20process%20will%20compound%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20democratic%20principles%20which%20happened%20due%20to%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20presiding%20officer%2C%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bench%2C%20the%20court%20is%20duty%20bound%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20democratic%20process%20is%20not%20set%20at%20naught%20by%20such%20subterfuge.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20therefore%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20Court%20must%20step%20in%20such%20exceptional%20circumstances%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20basic%20democratic%20mandate%20is%20ensured%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20AAP%20hail%20SC%20order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20reaction%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20AAP%20supremo%20and%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20thanked%20the%20court%20for%20saving%20democracy%20in%20these%20difficult%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20congratulated%20the%20new%20Chandigarh%20mayor%2C%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%2C%20and%20said%20that%20he%20hails%20from%20a%20poor%20family.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20victory%20became%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20SC.%20This%20is%20a%20victory%20of%20Indian%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Kumar%20was%20the%20Congress-AAP%20joint%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20saved%20Democracy%20from%20the%20fangs%20of%20an%20autocratic%20BJP%2C%20which%20resorted%20to%20dirty%20election%20manipulation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20institutional%20sabotage%20in%20the%20Chandigarh%20Mayor%20polls%20is%20only%20a%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%20in%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20devious%20conspiracy%20to%20trample%20Democracy.%20All%20Indians%20must%20fight%20this%20onslaught%20on%20our%20Constitution%2C%20collectively.%C2%A0Never%20forget.%20Our%20Democracy%20shall%20be%20at%20the%20crossroads%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections!%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20too%20reacted%20by%20saying%20that%20Masih%20was%20just%20a%20pawn%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20murder%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708428824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fblow-to-bjp-as-supreme-court-declares-aap-candidate-winner-of-chandigarh-mayoral-poll%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bench%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%20against%20presiding%20officer%20Anil%20Masih%2C%20and%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20told%20the%20court%20falsehoods%20in%20his%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Advance%20on%20Rafah%20Would%20Have%20%E2%80%98Dire%20Humanitarian%20Consequences%E2%80%99%3A%20Senior%20Gaza%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc