0desperate%20civilians%2C%20but%20also%20looting%20and%20criminalisation%2C%20is%20hampering%20efforts%20by%20the%20humanitarian%20community%E2%80%A6to%20deliver%20assistance%20to%20the%20people%20that%20actually%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20needs%20to%20be%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20Monday%2C%20UN%20Special%20Coordinator%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20Peace%20Process%2C%20Tor%20Wennesland%2C%20visited%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20he%20met%20with%20internally%20displaced%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20met%20with%20NGO%20and%20UN%20personnel%20the%20see%20the%20challenges%20they%20face%20first%20hand%2C%20including%20the%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%20which%20is%20impacting%20the%20distribution%20of%20humanitarian%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20clear%20that%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20UN%20Spokesperson%20Stephane%20Dujarric%20told%20correspondents%20in%20New%20York%20at%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsg%2Fen%2Fcontent%2Fossg%2Fnoon-briefing-highlight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregular%20press%20briefing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UN%20needs%20the%20tools%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20including%20the%20need%20for%20Israel%20to%20allow%20entry%20of%20items%20critical%20to%20UN%20operations%20and%20to%20improve%20deconfliction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContinued%20hostilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntense%20Israeli%20bombardment%20from%20air%2C%20land%20and%20sea%20continues%20across%20much%20of%20the%20war-torn%20enclave%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOCHA%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20resulting%20in%20further%20civilian%20casualties%2C%20displacement%2C%20and%20destruction%20of%20civilian%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidespread%20ground%20operations%20and%20heavy%20fighting%20between%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20Palestinian%20armed%20groups%20also%20continue%20to%20be%20reported%2C%20especially%20in%20Khan%20Younis%20and%20Deir%20al%20Balah%2C%20OCHA%20said%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fhostilities-gaza-strip-and-israel-flash-update-121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflash%20update%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%2017%20and%2019%20February%2C%20dozens%20of%20rockets%20were%20also%20reportedly%20fired%20by%20armed%20Palestinians%20toward%20Israel%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENasser%20hospital%20evacuations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20operation%20in%20the%20Nasser%20Hospital%20complex%20in%20Khan%20Younis%20have%20continued%2C%20OCHA%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20UN%20and%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20evacuated%2014%20patients.%20Negotiations%20are%20ongoing%20for%20the%20evacuation%20of%20the%20remaining%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20over%20180%20patients%20and%2015%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20remain%20inside%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20hospital%20is%20still%20experiencing%20an%20acute%20shortage%20of%20food%2C%20basic%20medical%20supplies%2C%20and%20oxygen.%20There%20is%20no%20tap%20water%20and%20no%20electricity%2C%20except%20a%20backup%20generator%20maintaining%20some%20lifesaving%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20WHO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Steep%20rise%E2%80%99%20in%20child%20malnutrition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20agencies%20on%20Monday%20warned%20of%20a%20steep%20rise%20in%20malnutrition%20among%20children%20and%20pregnant%20and%20breastfeeding%20women%2C%20posing%20grave%20threat%20to%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20especially%20serious%20in%20north%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20been%20almost%20completely%20cut%20off%20from%20aid%20for%20weeks%2C%20and%20where%20one%20in%20six%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20two%20is%20acutely%20malnourished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20not%20much%20better%20in%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20the%20UN%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNICEF%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20WHO%20and%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20(WFP)%2C%20said%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Fpress-releases%2Fchildrens-lives-threatened-rising-malnutrition-gaza-strip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rafah%2C%20where%20aid%20has%20been%20more%20available%2C%205%25%20of%20children%20under%20two%20are%20acutely%20malnourished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20clear%20evidence%20that%20access%20to%20humanitarian%20aid%20is%20needed%20and%20can%20help%20prevent%20the%20worst%20outcomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agencies%20said%2C%20reiterating%20the%20call%20to%20protect%20Rafah%20from%20the%20threat%20of%20intensified%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Bank%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCHA%20also%20reported%20further%20violent%20incidents%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20claiming%20both%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2016%20February%2C%20two%20Israeli%20men%20were%20shot%20and%20killed%20in%20southern%20Israel%2C%20and%20four%20others%20inclu