on%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20endorses%20taking%20a%20whole%20diet%20approach%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcardiologist-eats-breakfast-lunch-snacks-healthy-heart-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimproving%20heart%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20eat%20most%20of%20the%20time%20that%20matters.%20And%20you%20may%20be%20surprised%20by%20some%20of%20the%20foods%20that%20can%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey're%20cheap%2C%20and%20you%20might%20already%20have%20them%20in%20your%20cupboards%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20think%20that%20there%20are%20any%20superfoods.%20There%20are%20no%20kind%20of%20magic%20ingredients%20that%20you%20can%20put%20into%20your%20diet%20that%20will%20right%20all%20of%20the%20other%20wrongs%20that%20are%20in%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20OK%20to%20have%20the%20odd%20indulgent%20snack%20or%20meal%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20shows%20that%20eating%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fmediterranean-diet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Mediterranean-style%20diet%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20packed%20with%20colorful%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffiber-whole-grain-bread-better-heart-health-fruits-vegetables-study-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewhole%20grains%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nuts%2C%20seeds%2C%20lean%20proteins%2C%20and%20healthy%20fats%2C%20is%20the%20best%20diet%20for%20heart%20health%2C%20she%20said.%20Eating%20less%20red%20and%20processed%20meat%20is%20also%20a%20good%20idea%20because%20they%20contain%20lots%20of%20salt%20and%20saturated%20fat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20shared%20three%20surprising%20foods%20that%20are%20good%20for%20heart%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFrozen%20peas%C2%A0%3C%2Fh