_amedi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20in%20his%20Instagram%20post%20in%20Hebrew%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20doctors%20at%20the%20hospital%20calls%20me%20'360'%2C%20He%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20for%20people%20to%20think%20that%20if%20you%20have%20made%20a%20360-degree%20turn%20then%20you%20are%20back%20at%20the%20starting%20point%2C%20but%20with%20battle%20wounded%20the%20story%20is%20a%20little%20different.%20This%20trip%20through%20the%20sharp%2C%20flat%20and%20dull%20corners%20of%20life%2C%20of%20war%2C%20changes%20you%2C%20shapes%20you%20and%20through%20it%20you%20are%20reborn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20birthday%20sad%20second%20in%20two%20months.%20Thank%20God%20for%20all%20the%20gifts.%20And%20thanks%20to%20all%20the%20well-wishers%2C%20someday%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20thank%20you%20all%2C%20And%20to%20the%20life%20of%20adventures%20on%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmedi%20is%20best%20known%20for%20playing%20agent%20Sagi%20Tzur%20in%20%26quot%3BFauda%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Netflix%20drama%20about%20an%20elite%20undercover%20team%20trying%20to%20track%20down%20a%20notorious%20Palestinian%20terrorist.%20Amedi%20joined%20the%20cast%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20End%20In%20Sight'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20order%20a%20unilateral%20ceasefire%20and%20stop%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20troops%20are%20advancing%20south%20to%20take%20control%20of%20Rafah%2C%20which%20it%20calls%20the%20last%20bastion%20of%20Hamas.%20Over%201%20million%20Palestinians%20live%20in%20shelters%20and%20relief%20camps%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20rejected%20calls%20to%20spare%20Rafah%2C%20arguing%20that%20failing%20to%20launch%20the%20operation%20would%20mean%20%26quot%3Blosing%20the%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20the%20military%20says%20it%20is%20working%20to%20move%20civilians%20from%20the%20area%20to%20minimise%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air-ground%20assault%20in%20Gaza%20has%20killed%20over%2028%2C000%20people%2C%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%2C%20though%20Israel%20has%20contested%20the%20figures.%20The%20war%20began%20when%20Hamas%20attacked%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C100%20people%20and%20taking%20over%20250%20hostages%20and%20130%20presumed%20to%20be%20still%20in%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20vetoed%20the%20ceasefire%20resolution%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20has%20backed%20Israel%2C%20its%20longtime%20ally%2C%20with%20military%20and%20relief%20aid%20since%20the%20war%20began.%20The%20US%20veto%20threat%20remains%20in%20next%20week's%20possible%20UNSC%20vote.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708426020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fk1i89ggo_idan-amedi_625x300_09_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffauda-actor-idan-amedi-shares-1st-photo-of-injuries-he-received-during-gaza-op-5093394%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20full-scale%20military%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20has%20moved%20south%20and%20the%20defence%20forces%20are%20preparing%20to%20pound%20Rafah%2C%20the%20only%20border%20crossing%20with%20Egypt%20and%20a%20transit%20for%20humanitarian%20aid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffauda-actor-idan-amedi-shares-1st-photo-of-injuries-he-received-during-gaza-op-5093394%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffauda-actor-idan-amedi-shares-1st-photo-of-injuries-he-received-during-gaza-op-5093394%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffauda-actor-idan-amedi-shares-1st-photo-of-i