%5C%22%3EBTS%20tattoos%3A%20Decoding%20RM%2C%20Jungkook%2C%20Jimin%2C%20V%2C%20J-Hope%2C%20Suga%20and%20Jin's%20iconic%20designs%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLittle%20Entertainment...%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice's%20Comic%20Relief%20During%20Big%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20replay%20of%20the%20much-talked%20about%20video%20from%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20polls%20provided%20some%20comic%20relief%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20amid%20heated%20arguments%20and%20strong%20observations%20by%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20which%20has%20earlier%20drawn%20strong%20observations%20from%20the%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20was%20replayed%20in%20the%20court%20today%20after%20the%20bench%20examined%20ballot%20papers%20that%20were%20declared%20invalid%20during%20the%20January%2030%20election.%C2%A0As%20the%20video%20was%20played%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20all%20of%20them%20see%20the%20video.%20A%20little%20entertainment%20is%20good%20for%20everybody!%26quot%3B%C2%A0He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20petitioners%20have%20already%20specified%20the%20relevant%20part%20of%20the%20video%20and%20the%20entire%20clip%20need%20not%20be%20replayed.%20%26quot%3BOtherwise%20all%20of%20us%20will%20be%20here%20till%205.45%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20pulled%20up%20the%20returning%20officer%20for%20the%20election%2C%20Anil%20Masih%2C%20who%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20marking%20ballot%20papers%20after%20the%20vote.%20Mr%20Masih%20had%20declared%20as%20invalid%20eight%20votes%20in%20support%20of%20the%20AAP%20mayoral%20candidate.%20This%20ensured%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20BJP%20nominee%2C%20even%20though%20the%20party%20had%20lesser%20votes%20than%20the%20AAP-Congress%20combine.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20pulled%20up%20the%20officer%20and%20indicated%20that%20it%20may%20order%20a%20recount%20of%20votes%2C%20with%20those%20invalidated%20counted%20as%20valid.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20overturn%20the%20result%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20remarks%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20three%20AAP%20councillors%20switching%20to%20the%20BJP.%20This%20means%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20re-election%2C%20the%20BJP%20now%20has%20an%20edge%20over%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance.%20The%20court%20also%20noted%20after%20the%20switchovers%20that%20horsetrading%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20grilled%20the%20poll%20officer%2C%20questioning%20his%20actions%20caught%20on%20camera.%20Mr%20Masih%20had%20then%20claimed%20that%20he%20invalidated%20some%20ballot%20papers%20because%20they%20had%20been%20defaced.%20This%20afternoon%2C%20the%20court%20examined%20the%20ballot%20papers%20and%20said%20they%20had%20not%20been%20defaced.%20It%20said%20Mr%20Masih%20had%20misled%20the%20court.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20said%20the%20poll%20officer%20must%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20tampering%20with%20the%20ballot%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708424940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fot2q6i6o_chandigarh-poll-officer-1200_625x300_05_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-chandigarh-mayor-polls-little-entertainment-chief-justices-comic-relief-during-big-hearing-5093197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20replay%20of%20the%20much-talked%20about%20video%20from%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20polls%20provided%20some%20comic%20relief%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20amid%20heated%20arguments%20and%20strong%20observations%20by%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22