rst-of-its-kind%20Civic%20Media%20Lab%20in%20Lagos.%20Pierre%20then%20cofounded%20and%20was%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20NLA%20Ventures%2C%20where%20she%20invested%20in%20healthcare%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20met%20her%20Emmeline%20Ventures%20cofounders%2C%20Naseem%20Sayani%20and%20Azin%20Radsan%20Van%20Alebeek%2C%20while%20at%20a%2012-week%20investor%20boot%20camp%20focused%20on%20bringing%20more%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color%20to%20venture%20investing%20in%202020%2C%20and%20they%20launched%20the%20firm%20two%20years%20later.%20Pierre%20said%20she%20was%20influenced%20by%20how%20she%20was%20treated%20differently%20from%20her%20male%20counterparts%20while%20fundraising%20as%20the%20Sahara%20Reporters%20Media%20Group%20CEO.%20After%20that%20experience%2C%20she%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bchange%20the%20narrative%20and%20also%20be%20amongst%20the%20people%20who%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20underrepresented%20founders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENasir%20Qadree%2C%20Zeal%20Capital%20Partners%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225732%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nasir%20Qadree%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20Zeal%20Capital%20Partners.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca825f6fcb546d2d4eaaf3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224299%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENasir%20Qadree%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20partner%20of%20Zeal%20Capital%20Partners.%3Cp%3ENasir%20Qadree%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENotable%20investments%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEsusu%2C%20Humanly%2C%20Icon%20Savings%20Plan%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kinds%20of%20companies%20he%20invests%20in%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESeed%20and%20Series%20A%20startups%20in%20fintech%2C%20future%20of%20work%20and%20learning%2C%20and%20health%20equity%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20he's%20on%20the%20list%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQadree%20was%20eager%20to%20learn%20mor