%20Kremlin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fjailed-russian-activist-ilya-yashin-to-keep-fighting-tyranny-after-navalny-death%2Farticleshow%2F107850501.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fjailed-russian-activist-ilya-yashin-to-keep-fighting-tyranny-after-navalny-death%2Famp_articleshow%2F107850501.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fjailed-russian-activist-ilya-yashin-to-keep-fighting-tyranny-after-navalny-death%2Famp_articleshow%2F107850501.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%25%20Maratha%20Quota%20Gets%20Cross-Party%20Backing%20In%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20today%20unanimously%20passed%20the%20Maratha%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20a%20legislation%20that%20will%20grant%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20both%20education%20and%20government%20jobs.%20The%20Maharashtra%20State%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Bill%202024%2C%20once%20enacted%2C%20will%20undergo%20a%20thorough%20review%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20follows%20a%20comprehensive%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Backward%20Class%20Commission%2C%20based%20on%20a%20survey%20covering%20nearly%202.5%20crore%20families.%20This%20survey%20meticulously%20explores%20the%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20educational%20backwardness%20faced%20by%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Maratha%20community%20constitutes%20a%20significant%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20Maharashtra's%20population.%20%26quot%3BThe%20survey%20has%20been%20conducted%20on%20nearly%202-2.5%20crore%20people.%20On%20February%2020%2C%20we%20have%20called%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20after%20which%20Maratha%20reservation%20will%20be%20given%20according%20to%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20urgency%20for%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20bill%20was%20spurred%20by%20the%20hunger%20strike%20by%20Maratha%20quota%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%2C%20who%20commenced%20his%20protest%20on%20February%2010.%20Mr%20Jarange's%20persistent%20demand%20for%20a%20special%20legislative%20session%20to%20discuss%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20issue%20gained%20momentum%2C%20culminating%20in%20the%20recent%20tabling%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20new%20legislation%20is%20to%20address%20the%20economic%20struggles%20experienced%20by%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20The%20survey%20reveals%20that%2021.22%20per%20cent%20of%20Maratha%20families%20are%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20exceeding%20the%20state's%20average%20of%2017.4%20per%20cent.%20Additionally%2C%2084%20per%20cent%20of%20Maratha%20families%20do%20not%20fall%20under%20the%20'progressed'%20category%2C%20making%20them%20eligible%20for%20reservation%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20indicates%20that%2094%20per%20cent%20of%20farmer%20suicides%20in%20Maharashtra%20involve%20Maratha%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20attempts%20by%20state%20governments%20to%20introduce%20reservations%20for%20Marathas%20have%20faced%20legal%20challenges%2C%20with%20previous%20efforts%20being%20struck%20down%20by%20courts.%20However%2C%20the%20persistence%20of%20protests%20and%20the%20political%20significance%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community%20have%20led%20to%20repeated%20revivals%20of%20this%20sensitive%20issue%2C%20given%20that%20the%20community%20constitutes%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20Maharashtra's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jarange%20today%20said%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20if%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20grants%2010%20or%2020%20per%20cent%20reservation%20as%20long%20as%20the%20quota%20comes%20under%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20category%20and%20is%20not%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20giving%20us%20what%20we%20don't%20want.%20We%20want%20a%20reservation%20in%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20category%2C%20but%20they%20are%20giving%20us%20a%20separate%20quota%20instead.%20If%20the%20government%20doesn't%20discuss%20and%20implement%20the%20draft%20notification%20on%20the%20reservation%20for%20blood%20relatives%20of%20Kunbi%20Marathas%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20the%20course%20of%20the%20agitation%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20activist%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20separate%20reservation%20outside%20the%20OBC%20category%20might%20pose%20legal%20challenges%2C%20as%20it%20could%20exceed%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20reservation%20cap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20recently%20issued%20a%20draft%20notification%20allowing%20Maratha%20individuals%20to%20claim%20affiliation%20with%20the%20agrarian%20Kunbi%20community.%20According%20to%20the%20notification%2C%20if%20a%20Maratha%20person%20can%20provide%20documentary%20evidence%20of%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kunbi%20community%2C%20their%20blood%20relatives%20would%20also%20be%20eligible%20for%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates.%20The%20Kunbi%20community%20falls%20within%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20category%2C%20and%20this%20move%20has%20been%20met%20with%20both%20support%20and%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708422720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fp9sgdg94_shinde-fadnavis-650_625x300_04_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-reservation-bill-passed-in-maharashtra-assembly-5092654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maharashtr