ds.%20You%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they're%20getting%20more%20emotional%20support%2C%20which%20can%20mean%20another%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20bill%2C%20which%20can%20get%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20left%20Starbucks%20for%20Target%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20%244.10%20per%20hour%20raise%2C%20so%20it%20made%20things%20significantly%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20be%20able%20to%20help%20provide%20for%20my%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETarget%20fired%20me%20after%20I%20allowed%20one%20of%20my%20baristas%20to%20buy%20a%20Stanley%20x%20Starbucks%20cup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-workers-caught-off-guard-by-stanley-cup-crackdown-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20never%20even%20bought%20a%20Stanley%20cup%20for%20myself%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20hate%20the%20cups%20if%20we're%20being%20honest.%20I%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20the%20ugliest%20things%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20did%20let%20one%20of%20my%20team%20members%20purchase%20one.%20This%20barista%20was%20consistently%20closing%20with%20me%2C%20and%20when%20we'd%20have%20call-outs%20I%20could%20count%20on%20him%20to%20come%20in%20and%20help.%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20let%20him%20purchase%20a%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20thinking%20about%20how%20it%20was%20the%20night%20before%20the%20official%20January%203%20release%20date%2C%20because%20normally%20anything%20that%20isn%E2%80%99t%20supposed%20to%20be%20sold%20before%20a%20certain%20date%20won't%20even%20ring%20up%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20fired%20emotionally%20destroyed%20me%20because%20I'd%20spent%20the%20past%20eight%20months%20putting%20all%20of%20my%20time%20and%20energy%20basically%20rebuilding%20the%20store%E2%80%99s%20entire%20Starbucks%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20put%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20effort%2C%20and%20energy%20into%20getting%20this%20Starbucks%20up%20to%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20standard%20by%20myself%3A%20I%20had%20to%20hire%20people%2C%20I%20had%20to%20train%20them%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20do%20all%20of%20my%20own%20training%20and%20figure%20out%20the%20licensing%20rules%20on%20my%20own%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20being%20a%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20lost%20my%20job%2C%20that%20was%20it.%20All%20of%20my%20effort%20was%20for%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhile%20it%20destroyed%20me%20emotionally%2C%20it%20also%20risked%20destroying%20me%20financially%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20pay%20the%20COBRA%20premium%20to%20continue%20my%20Target%20insurance%2C%20so%20I%20applied%20for%20Medicaid%20as%20well%20as%20for%20unemployment%20and%20food%20stamps%20until%20I%20can%20get%20coverage%20sorted%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20I%20still%20have%20to%20pay%20my%20bills%3A%20I%20have%20a%20car%20payment%2C%20a%20mortgage%2C%20and%20my%20oldest%20child%20plays%20euphonium%2C%20so%20we%20pay%20for%20his%20instrument%20rental%20every%20month.%20It's%20not%20cheap%20but%20it's%20something%20he's%20very%20dedicated%20to%20and%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20let%20that%20go%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20savings%2C%20I%20had%20less%20than%20%241%2C000%20when%20I%20was%20terminated%2C%20and%20that%20is%20draining%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThis%20situation%20has%20me%20feeling%20severely%20depressed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20how%20much%20weight%20I%E2%80%99ve%20lost%2C%20but%20I%20know%20it's%20significant%20because%20my%20clothes%20feel%20looser%20on%20me.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20also%20been%20skipping%20meals%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20kids%20have%20enough%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20to%20well%20over%20100%20jobs%20in%20two%20weeks.%20I%20would%20go%20on%20Indeed.com%20and%20apply%20for%20every%20single%20job%20that%20I%20qualify%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20jobs%20I%20was%20overqualified%20for.%20I%20also%20went%20to%20the%20mall%20in%20my%20area%2C%20wrote%20down%20every%20single%20store%20there%2C%20and%20sent%20an%20application%20for%20each%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20two%20versions%20of%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3A%20one%20that%20shows%20all%20my%20qualifications%2C%20and%20then%20another%20for%20entry-level%20roles%20at%20places%20like%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20and%20Subway.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%E2%80%99ve%20applied%20for%20everything%20in%20a%2025-mile%20radius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I%20had%20some%20interviews%20and%20I%20even%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Walgreens%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20making%20%2419%20an%20hour%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20cut%20from%20the%20%2423.75%20I%20was%20earning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20could%20go%20back%20and%20change%20anything%2C%20I%20guess%20I%20would%20never%20have%20let%20my%20barista%20buy%20the%20cup.%20I%E2%80%99d%20try%20to%20educate%20myself%20better%20on%20the%20policy%20even%20though%20I've%20since%20looked%20at%20it%20more%20closely%20and%20it%20feels%20so%20vague.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-15-minute-rule-policy-stanley-cup-workers-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20does%20say%20they%20can%20terminate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20just%20doesn't%20seem%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I've%20seen%20during%20my%20time%20working%20at%20Target%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20company%20picks%20and%20chooses%20when%20to%20fully%20enforce%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20team%20is%20upset%20by%20how%20I%20was%20treated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20them%20quit%20after%20I%20was%20fired%20and%20others%20are%20looking%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20needs%20to%20be%20nine%20or%2010%20workers%20plus%20a%20team%20lead%20to%20operate%20my%20Starbucks%2C%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-stanley-cup-firings-lead-to-starbucks-cafe-understaffing-concerns-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%E2%80%99s%20in%20danger%20of%20not%20being%20in%20compliance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20they%20do%20get%20a%20new