eveland%20studio%20in%20November%20of%202019%2C%20freshly%20moved%20out%20of%20LA%2C%20rearing%20and%20ready%20to%20jump%20back%20in%20to%20pole%2C%20in%20a%20brand%20new%20community%20where%20she%20knew%20no%20one%20and%20no%20one%20knew%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20wasn't%20intimidated%20or%20anxious.%20The%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20the%20new%20kid%20on%20the%20block%20didn't%20bother%20her%20in%20the%20least.%20She%20immediately%20warmed%20to%20the%20studio%20and%20all%20the%20students%20with%20an%20effortless%20grace%2C%20and%20it%20soon%20felt%20as%20if%20she%20had%20always%20been%20apart%20of%20the%20studio%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fundraising%20page%20also%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20all%20of%20her%20many%20impressive%20accomplishments%20and%20talents%2C%20Kagney%20struggled%20with%20mental%20health%20issues%20as%20the%20years%20passed%20by.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20alone%20as%20she%20undoubtedly%20felt%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20her%20own%20head%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20show%20up%20for%20her%20friends%20and%20the%20community%20that%20cared%20about%20her.%20She%20fought%20her%20own%20battles%20with%20the%20same%20tenacity%20and%20drive%20she%20showed%20in%20every%20other%20area%20of%20her%20life%2C%20with%20as%20much%20strength%20as%20she%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GoFundMe%20page%2C%20set%20up%20by%20her%20former%20trainers%2C%20confirmed%20Kagney%20died%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKagney%20entered%20the%20adult%20film%20industry%20in%20the%20mid-2000s%20but%20returned%20to%20Ohio%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20establishing%20a%20pole%20fitness%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20her%20career%2C%20Karter%20achieved%20several%20awards%20and%20received%20numerous%20AVN%20award%20nominations%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20her%20IMDb%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708421580000%2C%22vi