son-to-build-second-hotel-in-ayodhya-with-easemytrip-jeewani-group-124022000476_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fradisson-to-build-second-hotel-in-ayodhya-with-easemytrip-jeewani-group-124022000476_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Final%20Offer%2C%20INDIA%20Unity%20In%20UP%20Hinges%20On%20Congress%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20signs%20of%20fresh%20trouble%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20have%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%20The%20Akhilesh%20Yadav-led%20party%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20made%20a%20final%20offer%20of%2017%20seats%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20accept%20it.%20Mr%20Yadav%20has%20so%20far%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20which%20is%20moving%20through%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20said%20his%20party%20will%20join%20the%20yatra%20once%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20drive%20a%20hard%20bargain%20in%20the%20politically%20significant%20state.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20had%20first%20offered%2011%20seats%20to%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%20But%20with%20the%20Jayant%20Chaudhary-led%20Rastriya%20Lok%20Dal%20switching%20to%20the%20NDA%20camp%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20agreed%20to%20give%2015%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20latter%20bargained%20for%20more%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party%20offered%20Saharanpur%20and%20Amroha%20seats%20too%2C%20reportedly%20on%20the%20request%20of%20Congress's%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20Then%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20Congress%20asked%20for%20Moradabad%20or%20Bijnor%20seat.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20put%20its%20foot%20down%20on%20a%20final%2017-seats%20offer%2C%20and%20the%20talks%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20several%20rounds%20of%20discussions%2C%20exchanged%20many%20lists.%20When%20the%20seat-sharing%20is%20done%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20will%20participate%20in%20their%20Nyay%20yatra%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20yesterday.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20waiting%20for%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20Congress%20leadership.%20Mr%20Yadav%20wants%20the%20Congress%20to%20reply%20before%20the%20first%20leg%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Yatra%20ends.%20If%20Congress%20does%20not%20seal%20the%20deal%20in%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20the%20alliance%20is%20likely%20to%20fall%20apart%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20tussle%20between%20the%20allies%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20spokesperson%20Fakhrul%20Hassan%20Chand%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20responsible%20if%20the%20alliance%20gets%20derailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%20addressed%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20our%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20large-hearted%2C%20but%20your%20petty%20and%20vain%20functionaries%20do%20not%20want%20an%20alliance%20between%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20If%20the%20alliance%20falls%20apart%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20be%20responsible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20should%20remember%20that%20its%20vote-share%20is%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20many%20small%20parties.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20strong%20enough%20to%20remove%20the%20anti-people%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20announced%20candidates%20for%2016%20out%20of%2080%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20underlining%20that%20it%20does%20not%20need%20Congress's%20clearance%20to%20name%20its%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20won%20five%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20the%202019%20polls.%20The%20Congress%20won%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMany%20INDIA%20Setbacks%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impasse%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20comes%20after%20the%20Congress's%20push%20for%20more%20seats%20derailed%20alliance%20talks%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20that%20her%20party%20will%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20state%20Congress%20leadership%20insisted%20on%20at%20least%2010%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20offering%20two.%20In%20damage%20control%20mode%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20said%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20but%20no%20formal%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20has%20been%20announced%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20have%20decided%20to%20contest%20separately.%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20mutual%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20hostility%20between%20the%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20among%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%20who%20have%20pushed%20for%20greater%20role%20for%20regional%20parties%20in%20their%20strongholds.%20%26quot%3BIn%20many%20states%2C%20the%20Congress%20doesn't%20exist%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20regional%20parties%20are%20fighting%20tooth%20and%20nail%20against%20the%20saffron%20camp%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20they%20will%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20pushing%20for%20more%20seats%20in%20states%20dominated%20by%20regional%20forces%2C%20but%20not%20returning%20the%20favour%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20strongholds.%20The%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20JDU%20had%20also%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20after%20it%20switched%20to%20the%20NDA%20camp.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20had%20decided%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20elections%20after%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath's%20%26quot%3BAkhilesh%20Vakhilesh%26quot%3B%20remark.%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20then%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20continues%20to%20behave%20like%20this%2C%20then%20who%20will%20trust%20them%3F%20If%20we%20fight%20with%20confusion%20in%20mind%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20then%20we%20won't%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708420680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F4hp09k9g_rahul-akhilesh-split_625x300_20_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-samajwadi-party-india-akhilesh-yadavs-final-offer-india-unity-in-up-hinges-on-congress-reply-5092902%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20signs%20of%20fresh%20trouble%20for%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20have%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-samajwadi-party-india-akhilesh-yadavs-final-offer-india-unity-in-up-hinges-on-congress-reply-5092902%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-samajwadi-party-india-akhilesh-yadavs-final-offer-india-unity-in-up-hinges-on-congress-reply-5092902%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-samajwadi-party-india-akhilesh-yadavs-final-offer-india-unity-in-up-hinges-on-congress-reply-5092902%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Europe%2C%20you%20ready%3F'%20Usher%20announces%20London%20shows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708420620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-usher-alicia-keys_6461999.jpg%3F20240220104112%22%2C%22originI