iety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fshikun-review-1235916632%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal's%20Shock%20RCB%20Release%2C%20Ex-Director's%20Big%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20(RCB)%20Director%20of%20Cricket%2C%20Mike%20Hesson%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20franchise's%20decision%20to%20release%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202022.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202022%20mega%20auction%2C%20RCB%20retained%20three%20players%20--%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Glenn%20Maxwell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1423-glenn-maxwell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGlenn%20Maxwell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20Siraj.%20RCB's%20decision%20to%20release%20Chahal%20came%20as%20a%20big%20shock%20and%20the%20leg-spinner%20was%20eventually%20bought%20by%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20during%20the%20auctions.%20Hesson%2C%20who%20was%20with%20RCB%20at%20that%20time%2C%20recalled%20that%20he%20personally%20called%20Chahal%20to%20explain%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20ouster%20from%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hesson%20revealed%20that%20Chahal%20was%20%26quot%3Bupset%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdisinterested%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYuzi%20was%20communicated%20with%20a%20huge%20amount.%20And%20I%20know%20that%20because%20I%20was%20the%20guy%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20phone.%20I%20remember%20ringing%20Yuzi%20afterwards%20and%20he%20was%20upset.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20try%20and%20explain%20the%20auction%20dynamics%20to%20him%20at%20that%20time.%20He%20was%20visibly%20disinterested%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20blame%20him.%20He%20was%20an%20RCBian%20and%20he%20was%20frustrated.%20But%20I%20can%20assure%20everyone%20that%20he%20is%20well-aware%20of%20the%20issues%20we%20were%20confronted%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Hesson%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaS331lScaXI%5C%22%3ECricket.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20it%20was%20a%20mega%20auction%2C%20Chahal%20did%20not%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20marquee%20players%20list.%20His%20name%20popped%20up%20after%2064%20players%20went%20under%20the%20hammer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHesson%20revealed%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20buy%20back%20Chahal%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harshal%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1293-harshal-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarshal%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20auction%2C%20but%20with%20the%20auction%20being%20a%20mega%20one%2C%20things%20got%20a%20bit%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20RCB%20did%20manage%20to%20buy%20back%20Harshal%2C%20Chahal%20eventually%20went%20to%20RR.%20As%20his%20replacement%2C%20RCB%20did%20manage%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20Sri%20Lanka%20all-rounder%20Wanindu%20Hasaranaga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20Yuzi%20(Yuzvendra%20Chahal)%20obviously%20when%20we%20did%20the%20initial%20retention%20and%20we%20only%20retained%20three%20players%20because%20we%20felt%20we%20wanted%20to%20try%20and%20buy%20back%20both%20Harshal%20Patel%20and%20Yuzi%20at%20the%20auction.%20Probably%20the%20thing%20that%20I'm%20really%20frustrated%20about%20even%20now%20is%20as%20you%20said%20Yuzi%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20top-five%20players%20of%20all%20time%20for%20RCB%20but%20he%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ever%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20couldn't%20make%20the%20top%20two%20marquee%20lists%20at%20that%20time%20was%20ridiculous%2C%20the%20fact%20t