%2C%20workers%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20saw%20the%20greatest%20decline%20between%202018-19%20and%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PLFS%20was%20launched%20by%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20Office%20in%20April%202017.%20It%20e%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estimates%20the%20key%20employment%20and%20unemployment%20indicators%20such%20as%20Worker%20Population%20Ratio%2C%20Labour%20Force%20Participation%20Rate%2C%20and%20Unemployment%20Rate.%20It%20further%20measures%20the%20employment%20status%20among%20social%20and%20religious%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20business%20daily%2C%20while%2022.1%25%20workers%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20worked%20as%20wage%20employees%20in%202018-19%2C%20the%20share%20fell%20to%2015.3%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20marking%20a%206.8%20percentage%20point%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20the%20population%20belonging%20to%20the%20Christian%20community%20saw%20a%203.2%20percentage%20point%20decline%2C%20as%20only%2028%25%20of%20Christian%20workers%20had%20regular%20jobs%20in%202022-23%2C%20down%20from%2031.2%25%20in%202018-19%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20followed%20by%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20as%20it%20saw%20a%202.5%20percentage%20point%20decline.%20Only%2026%25%20Sikh%20workers%20had%20wage%20employment%20in%202022-23%2C%20down%20from%2028.5%25%20in%202018-19%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20comparison%2C%20deterioration%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20employment%20is%20the%20least%20for%20the%20majority%20Hindu%20community.%20Here%2C%2021.4%25%20workers%20had%20regular%20salaried%20jobs%20in%202022-23%2C%20down%20by%202.3%20percentage%20points%20from%2023.7%25%20in%202018-19%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20daily%20further%20reported%20that%20while%20self-employment%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20across%20all%20religious%20groups%2C%20the%20share%20of%20casual%20workers%20has%20gone%20up%20only%20in%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2026.3%25%20Muslim%20workers%20worked%20as%20casual%20labourers%20in%202022-23%2C%20up%20from%2025.7%25%20in%202018-19.%20This%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20other%20religious%20groups%20like%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%20and%20Christians%2C%20which%20have%20seen%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20share%20of%20population%20working%20as%20casual%20labourers%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fstory%2F2178660%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fstory%2F2178660%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dstory%2F2178660%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fstory%2F2178667%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fstory%2F2178667%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dstory%2F2178667%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fstory%2F2178674%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fsto