0Verve%20talent%20agency%20after%20a%20little%20more%20than%20a%20year%20as%20CEO%20and%2014%20years%20after%20he%20helped%20launch%20the%20literary%20boutique%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Endeavor%E2%80%99s%20takeover%20of%20the%20William%20Morris%20Agency.%20The%20parting%20was%20confirmed%20late%20Monday%20by%20Verve%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thank%20Bill%20as%20a%20co-founder%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Cynthia%20Littleton%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fbill-weinstein-verve-talent-agency-out-1235916578%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fbill-weinstein-verve-talent-agency-out-1235916578%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fbill-weinstein-verve-talent-agency-out-1235916578%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legal%20Foundations%20of%20the%20World%20Are%20Collapsing%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20114741%2FGGjqkDTXsAARvAT.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20article%20in%20a%20two-part%20series.%20Read%20part%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flaw-and-humanity-buried-in-gaza-rubble%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Geneva%20Conventions%20which%20lay%20down%20the%20laws%20of%20war%20have%20a%20long%20history%2C%20but%20their%20most%20recent%20incarnations%20date%20from%20the%20years%20after%20World%20War%20II.%20Three%20existing%20conventions%20were%20updated%20to%20stipulate%20the%20minimal%20standards%20applicable%20to%20the%20treatment%20of%20prisoners%20of%20war%2C%20and%20the%20protection%20of%20medical%20sites%20during%20times%20of%20conflict.%20A%20fourth%20convention%20was%20added%2C%20extending%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20protections%20to%20civilians%20in%20times%20of%20armed%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20agreed%20in%201948%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20mass%20murder%20on%20an%20industrial%20scale%20never%20again%20occurred.%20The%20immediate%20context%20was%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20and%20the%20cruel%20premeditation%20and%20intent%20behind%20Nazi%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20plan%20for%20the%20extermination%20of%20European%20Jewry.%20But%20other%20horrors%20from%20the%20time%2C%20such%20as%20the%20genocide%20of%20Armenians%20by%20the%20Ottoman%20Turks%2C%20were%20actively%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Refugees%20Convention%20agreed%201951%20and%20made%20globally%20applicable%20through%20a%20protocol%20added%20in%201967%2C%20was%20another%20response%20to%20European%20traumas.%20In%20its%20early%20conception%2C%20it%20was%20a%20safeguard%20against%20the%20turmoil%20arising%20from%20mass%20population%20movements%20in%20Europe%20between%20the%20world%20wars%2C%20when%20the%20collapse%20of%20three%20multinational%20empires%20created%20politically%20unsettled%20conditions%2C%20fuelling%20efforts%20by%20various%20ethnic%20groups%20to%20carve%20out%20exclusive%20territories%20and%20purge%20these%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20country%20has%20been%20as%20consistent%20in%20the%20violation%20of%20these%20conventions%20than%20Israel.%20Its%20genocidal%20origins%20as%20a%20nation%20that%20denies%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20long%20settled%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20a%20land%20it%20seeks%20to%20colonise%2C%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fland-without-people-transfer-Palestinians%2Fdp%2F0571191002%5C%22%3Ewritten%20about%20authoritatively%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20extensively.%20The%20ICJ%20ruling%20of%20January%2026%20gives%20expression%20to%20the%20grim%20consequences%20of%20that%20embedded%20character%20of%20the%20Zionist%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%20of%20its%20creation%2C%20Israel%20expelled%20an%20estimated%20700%2C000%20Palestinians%20from%20their%20places%20of%20residence.%20Many%20ended%20up%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20did%20not%20fall%20to%20Israel%20because%20of%20the%20resolute%20defence%20of%20Egyptian%20and%20allied%20Palestinian%20forces.%20In%201948%2C%20by%20Resolution%20194%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20demanded%20that%20Israel%20should%20permit%20the%20return%20of%20all%20refugees%20or%20pay%20out%20appropriate%20levels%20of%20compensation.%20The%20Refugees%20Convention%20was%20not%20in%20force%20at%20the%20time%20and%20has%20since%20becoming%20operative%2C%20been%20inapplicable%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20refugees%2C%20whose%20status%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20numerous%20other%20UN%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20December%202022%2C%20the%20UN%20recalled%20all%20its%20resolutions%20on%20the%20issue%20since%201948%2C%20and%20placed%20on%20record%20its%20awareness%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgrowing%20needs%E2%80%9D%20of%20Palestinian%20refugees%20across%20the%20whole%20region%2C%20and%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20concern%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20difficult%20situation%20of%20the%20Palestine%20refugees%20under%20occupation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20humanitarian%20situation%20and%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20Palestine%20refugees%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20noted%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20regret%20that%20repatriation%20or%20compensation%20of%20the%20refugees%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20required%20by%20the%201948%20resolution%20had%20not%20been%20effected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20of%20return%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20refugees%20is%20a%20recognised%20aspect%20of%20international%20law.%20Israel%20played%20along%20with%20the%20demand%20when%20it%20was%20first%20formulated%20since%20it%20was%20a%20condition%20of%20its%20admission%20into%20the%20U.N.%20Once%20membership%20of%20the%20world%20body%20was%20secured%2C%20Israel%20shut%20the%20door.%20In%20public%20statements%20in%20the%20native%20language%20since%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20political%20leadership%20has%20absolutely%20ruled%20out%20any%20possible%20return%20of%20the%20refugees%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20fatal%20threat%20to%20the%20ethnic%20purity%20of%20the%20Zionist%20nation%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FBiggest-Prison-Earth-Occupied-Territories%2Fdp%2F1851685871%5C%22%3EIlan%20Pappe%2C%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20175).%20When%20speaking%20in%20English%20or%20addressing%20a%20global%20audience%2C%20Israeli%20spokespersons%20have%20blamed%20the%20victim%2C%20accusing%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20the%20undying%20urge%20to%20wage%20war%20and%20destroy%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpulsions%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20lands%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20daily%20reality%20of%20Palestinian%20life%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%201967%20war%20of%20aggression%20brought%20all%20of%20the%20territory%20between%20the%20river%20and%20the%20sea%20under%20Israeli%20military%20overlordship.%20Violations%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20have%20become%20routinised%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20they%20have%20become%20expected%20behaviour%20from%20Israel.%20Early%20during%20the%20current%20assault%20on%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Al-Ahli%20Baptist%20Hospital%20in%20the%20north%20was%20bombed.%20Soon%20afterwards%2C%20with%20little%20evidence%20available%2C%20Biden%20blamed%20the%20criminal%20act%20on%20a%20Palestinian%20rogue%20operation.%20That%20emboldened%20the%20Israeli%20side%20to%20destroy%20every%20one%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20medical%20facilities%20in%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed.%20Al-Shifa%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20largest%20hospital%2C%20was%20occupied%20mid-November%20and%20its%20director%20taken%20into%20Israeli%20custody.%20Over%20the%20next%20ten%20days%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-army-destroys-critical-utilities-structures-at-al-shifa-hospital-as-troops-leave-compound%2F3063792%23%3A~%3Atext%3DGAZA%2520CITY%252C%2520Palestine%2Cafter%252010%2520days%2520of%2520occupation.%5C%22%3Edestroyed%20vital%20medical%20equipment%20and%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20forced%20the%20evacuation%20of%20all%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20has%20been%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20narrative%2C%20a%20Hamas%20control%20centre%20where%20sinister%20terror%20acts%20are%20plotted%20in%20an%20underlying%20network%20of%20tunnels.%20It%20is%20a%20story-line%20that%20even%20the%20credulous%20U.S.%20media%20has%20had%20difficulty%20swallowing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F21%2Fal-shifa-hospital-gaza-hamas-israel%2F%5C%22%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20December%2023%2C%20found%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20claims%20collapsing%20at%20the%20slightest%20scrutiny.%20There%20was%20nothing%20to%20suggest%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20found%2C%20that%20the%20Al-Shifa%20tunnels%20were%20not%20for%20anything%20but%20routine%20storage%20and%20internal%20transportation%20of%20kit%20and%20equipment.%20The%20rooms%20connected%20to%20the%20tunnel%20network%20%E2%80%9Cshowed%20no%20immediate%20evidence%20of%20military%20use%E2%80%9D.%20None%20of%20the%20five%20hospital%20buildings%20identified%20as%20Hamas%20control%20centres%20%E2%80%9Cappeared%20connected%20to%20the%20tunnel%20network%E2%80%9D%2C%20nor%20was%20there%20any%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20that%20the%20tunnels%20could%20be%20accessed%20from%20inside%20hospital%20wards%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenocidal%20propaganda%20never%20concedes%20an%20argument%20to%20fact.%20As%20Israel%20ramped%20up%20for%20%E2%80%9Cabsolute%20victory%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20expert%20quoted%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20offered%20a%20reading%20of%20its%20motives.%20All%20the%20fake%20images%20and%20information%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%2C%20said%20this%20former%20US%20State%20Department%20official%2C%20constituted%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpre-excuse%20(for)%20future%20operations%20against%20hospitals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDehumanising%20propaganda%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20following%20the%20destruction%20of%20Al-Shifa%2C%20that%20rationale%20for%20a%20plan%20to%20create%20an%20uninhabitable%20wasteland%2C%20was%20fully%20exploited%20in%20the%20destruction%20of%20every%20medical%20facility%20in%20Gaza.%20Late-January%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20laid%20siege%20to%20the%20Al-Amal%20and%20Nasser%20hospitals%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20town%20of%20Khan%20Yunis.%20Patients%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%20victims%20of%20Israeli%20bombing%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20were%20ordered%20evacuated.%20Weeks%20later%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fabandoned-babies-found-decomposing-gaza-hospital-evacuated-rcna127533%5C%22%3Ebodies%20of%20abandoned%20babies%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20found%20in%20some%20hospitals%20in%20an%20advanced%20state%20of%20decomposition.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fytirawi%2Fstatus%2F1757353408481157197%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ERecordings%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20Israeli%20soldiers%20using%20the%20most%20demeaning%20terms%20as%20they%20ordered%20out%20patients%20and%20hospital%20staff%20through%20megaphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20global%20audiences%2C%20Israel%20has%20found%20means%20to%20dehumanise%20the%20Palestinians%20as%20a%20people%20and%20delegitimise%20their%20resistance%20in%20every%20possible%20way.%20First%20came%20the%20claim%20that%20Hamas%20militants%20had%20bound%20and%20trussed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.declassifieduk.org%2Fbeheaded-babies-how-uk-media-reported-israels-fake-news-as-fact%2F%5C%22%3E40%20babies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20before%20beheading%20them%20during%20their%20raid%20into%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20That%20claim%2C%20eagerly%20embraced%20by%20the%20Biden%20bunch%2C%20was%20soon%20proven%20false%2C%20though%20without%20any%20manner%20of%20a%20formal%20retraction%20from%20those%20who%20put%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20was%20quick%20to%20move%20on%20with%20its%20tested%20propaganda%20technique%3A%20to%20pin%20a%20concocted%20atrocity%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20demand%20that%20the%20world%20join%20in%20condemnation%2C%20with%20the%20accusation%20of%20anti-Semitism%20kept%20in%20reserve%2C%20to%20be%20hurled%20at%20all%20who%20refused%20to%20play%20along.%20Late-November%2C%20the%20Prime%20Ministers%20of%20Belgium%20and%20Spain%20travelled%20to%20the%20war%20zone%2C%20and%20while%20addressing%20the%20media%20at%20the%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2023%2Fnov%2F24%2Fspanish-and-belgian-prime-ministers-call-for-permanent-ceasefire-in-gaza-at-rafah-crossing-video%5C%22%3Edescribed%20as%20unacceptable%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdestruction%20of%20Gaza%20as%20a%20society%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Netanyahu%20was%20swift%20with%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsraeliPM%2Fstatus%2F1728080294735966359%5C%22%3Econdemnation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20formally%20kicked%20off%20the%20next%20phase%20in%20the%20propaganda%20war%20with%20accusations%20of%20sexual%20brutality%20and%20mass%20rapes%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20early%20December%2C%20following%20a%20cue%20from%20Netanyahu%2C%20Biden%20was%20roused%20to%20action%20across%20many%20time%20zones.%20Netanyahu%20spoke%20in%20Hebrew%20through%20most%20of%20his%20press%20conference%20that%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fnetanyahu-biden-slam-global-silence-on-hamas-sexual-violence-against-israeli-women%2F%5C%22%3Ebut%20switched%20to%20English%20at%20a%20strategic%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20say%20to%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20organisations%2C%20to%20the%20human%20rights%20organisations%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20heard%20of%20the%20rape%20of%20Israeli%20women%2C%20horrible%20atrocities%2C%20sexual%20mutilation%3F%20Where%20the%20hell%20are%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20width%20of%20the%20world%2C%20at%20a%20fund-raising%20event%20for%20his%20re-election%20bid%2C%20Biden%20curiously%20found%20words%20that%20almost%20echoed%20Netanyahu%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20on%20all%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20government%2C%20international%20organisations%2C%20civil%20society%20and%20businesses%20%E2%80%94%20to%20forcefully%20condemn%20the%20sexual%20violence%20of%20Hamas%20terrorists%20without%20equivocation%E2%80%9D.%20While%20trotting%20out%20a%20litany%20of%20horror%20porn%20stories%20about%20mass%20rapes%20and%20the%20mutilation%20of%20the%20feminine%20body%20Israeli%20government%20spokesmen%20and%20media%20were%20loud%20in%20demanding%20condemnation%20from%20the%20UN%20and%20other%20global%20bodies.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F28%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Foct-7-attacks-hamas-israel-sexual-violence.html%5C%22%3EOn%20December%2028%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20came%20out%20with%20the%20story%2C%20anchored%20by%20Pulitzer%20awardee%20Jeffrey%20Gettleman%2C%20that%20instantly%20became%20the%20most%20widely%20cited%20documentation%20of%20gender%20crimes%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20that%20it%20did%20not%20take%20long%20for%20the%20story%20to%20fall%20apart.%20The%20witnesses%20cited%20in%20the%20story%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMaxBlumenthal%2Fstatus%2F1740641517847335009%5C%22%3Eproved%20to%20have%20made%20contrary%20statements%20on%20the%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20various%20media%20outlets%20in%20the%20days%20after%20October%207.%20The%20family%20of%20one%20of%20the%20purported%20victims%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.com%2Fnode%2F2436331%2Fmedia%5C%22%3Erejected%20the%20main%20findings%20of%20the%20story%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20roiled%20by%20questions%20within%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2024%2F01%2F28%2Fnew-york-times-daily-podcast-camera%2F%5C%22%3Ecancelled%20a%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20scheduled%20to%20explore%20further%20unreported%20nuances%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20thorough%20dismantling%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthegrayzone.com%2F2024%2F01%2F10%2Fquestions-nyt-hamas-rape-report%2F%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20journalists%20Aaron%20Mate%20and%20Max%20Blumenthal%20from%20the%20Grayzone%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20demanding%20explanations%20for%20a%20report%20%E2%80%9Cmarred%20by%20sensationalism%2C%20wild%20leaps%20of%20logic%2C%20and%20an%20absence%20of%20concrete%20evidence%20to%20support%20its%20sweeping%20conclusion%E2%80%9D.%20That%20explanation%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20proffered%2C%20though%20Gettleman%2C%20a%20former%20Chief%20of%20Bureau%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdawnmclancy%2Fstatus%2F1756034583684854248%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ehas%20since%20gone%20on%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20his%20role%20as%20a%20journalist%20is%20to%20document%2C%20and%20not%20to%20gather%20evidence%2C%20since%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20is%20almost%20like%20the%20legal%20term%20that%20suggests%20you%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20prove%20an%20allegation%20or%20prove%20a%20case%20in%20court%E2%80%9D.%20It%20was%20yet%20another%20spurious%20justification%20for%20a%20report%20that%20has%20been%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40melaniesusans%2Fdeconstructing-screams-without-words-58260a824d70%5C%22%3Emaster%20class%20in%20crappy%20journalism%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20an%20established%20pattern%2C%20this%20propaganda%20effort%20never%20quite%20made%20the%20transition%20out%20of%20the%20world%20of%20innuendo%20and%20concoction%20into%20the%20realm%20of%20verification.%20A%20U.N.%20inquiry%20into%20mass%20crimes%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Israel%20had%20not%20quite%20got%20off%20the%20ground%20before%20it%20came%20under%20scathing%20fire%20from%20Israeli%20spokespersons.%20Israeli%20medical%20staff%20and%20other%20first%20responders%20with%20information%20potentially%20relevant%20to%20the%20inquiries%20were%20directed%20not%20to%20cooperate%20with%20a%20Commission%20supposedly%20suffused%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fgovernment-forbids-doctors-from-speaking-to-un-group-investigating-oct-7-atrocities%2F%5C%22%3Eanti-Semitic%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20front%20in%20the%20war%20on%20global%20opinion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20opened%20another%20front%20against%20the%20UN%20soon%20after%20the%20ICJ%E2%80%99s%20preliminary%20findings%20in%20the%20genocide%20hearing.%20The%20target%20this%20time%20was%20the%20UN%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20(UNRWA)%2C%20created%20in%201949%20to%20provide%20essential%20social%20services%20and%20humanitarian%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20refugee%20population.%20UNRWA%20activities%20now%20extend%20to%20refugee%20camps%20in%20Syria%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza.%20For%20Israel%2C%20UNRWA%20is%20a%20constant%20reminder%20of%20its%20war%20crimes%20from%20the%20moment%20of%20its%20birth.%20Within%20two%20days%20of%20the%20ICJ%20ruling%2C%20Israel%20declared%2C%20based%20on%20the%20interrogation%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%2C%20that%2012%20UNRWA%20staffers%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20No%20proof%20of%20any%20sort%20was%20put%20forward%2C%20but%20UNRWA%20moved%20quickly%20to%20suspend%20seven%20of%20the%20personnel%20identified%20by%20Israel.%20The%20others%20remained%20untraceable%20and%20had%20perhaps%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20attacks%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20western%20allies%2C%20which%20also%20happen%20to%20the%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20principal%20funders%2C%20jumped%20to%20do%20its%20bidding.%20The%20agency%2C%20which%20is%20a%20vital%20lifeline%20for%20the%20entire%20Gaza%20population%2C%20was%20effectively%20crippled%20by%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20support%2C%20left%20without%20the%20means%20of%20sustaining%20its%20operations%20beyond%20early-March.%20Welcoming%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20cabal%20of%20western%20powers%20led%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20denounced%20UNRWA%20as%20a%20body%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newarab.com%2Fnews%2Fwhy-israel-trying-destroy-unrwa%5C%22%3Eperpetuates%20the%20refugee%20issue%2C%20obstructs%20peace%2C%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20civilian%20arm%20of%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20problem%20with%20UNRWA%20in%20other%20words%2C%20is%20simply%20that%20it%20is%20a%20constant%20reminder%20that%20Israel%20was%20born%20in%20an%20ethnic%20cleansing%20that%20it%20has%20since%20perpetuated%20and%20aggravated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20the%20Zionist%20regime%20sees%20the%20end-point%20of%20the%20current%20phase%20of%20conflict%20is%20unclear.%20Early%20in%20the%20days%20of%20the%20brutal%20slaughter%2C%20the%20US%20moved%20an%20aircraft-carrier%20battle%20group%20to%20the%20Eastern%20Mediterranean%20in%20an%20obvious%20signal%20of%20support%20for%20Israel.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20the%20US%20made%20a%20public%20announcement%2C%20breaching%20its%20classification%20rules%2C%20that%20a%20submarine%20armed%20with%20nuclear%20missiles%20had%20been%20dispatched%20to%20the%20same%20stretch%20of%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20show%20of%20force%20in%20support%20of%20genocide%20is%20acceptable%20as%20part%20of%20the%20public%20engagement%20by%20the%20US%20in%20the%20region%2C%20what%20possibly%20could%20be%20the%20nature%20of%20its%20private%20counsels%20to%20both%20sides%3F%20These%20can%20only%20be%20guessed%20at%2C%20though%20what%20is%20known%20in%20public%20is%20that%20the%20heads%20of%20state%20of%20both%20Egypt%20and%20Jordan%2C%20soon%20after%20a%20visit%20from%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Anthony%20Blinken%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpalestinian-jordan-egypt-israel-refugee-502c06d004767d4b64848d878b66bd3d%5C%22%3Eabsolutely%20rejected%20any%20possibility%20of%20taking%20in%20refugees%20from%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20assault%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20instinct%2C%20in%20conflict%20indeed%2C%20with%20the%20implicit%20demands%20of%20the%20Refugees%20Convention.%20In%20the%20specific%20circumstances%20of%20Palestine%2C%20it%20presents%20a%20cruel%20dilemma%20to%20neighbouring%20Arab%20states%3A%20to%20either%20play%20along%20with%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20which%20could%20be%20the%20largest%20ever%2C%20or%20connive%20in%20the%20mass%20murder%20of%20innocents.%20For%20the%20world%20beyond%2C%20this%20is%20perhaps%20a%20moment%20of%20inflection%2C%20when%20the%20legal%20foundations%20on%20which%20a%20world%20order%20was%20built%20finally%20collapse.%20Its%20credentials%20were%20always%20dubious%2C%20but%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20global%20order%2C%20the%20sole%20superpower%2C%20now%20stands%20irretrievably%20exposed%20as%20a%20racially%20bigoted%20and%20duplicitous%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsukumar-muralidharan%5C%22%3ESukumar%20Muralidharan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20independent%20writer%20and%20researcher%20based%20in%20the%20Delhi%20region.%20He%20has%20worked%20in%20print%20media%2C%20as%20a%20journalism%20instructor%20and%20trainer%2C%20and%20press%20freedom%20campaigner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708409914000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20114741%2FGGjqkDTXsAARvAT.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%