%20first%20innings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Messi%20defends%20HK%20absence%20as%20backlash%20continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708407437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5DD3%2Fproduction%2F_132691042_gettyimages-2014062540.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68345107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20football%20superstar%20has%20addressed%20Chinese%20fans%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20Weibo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A190%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68345107%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68345107.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68345107.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MSC%202024%3A%20No%20International%20Security%20Without%20the%20Global%20South%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F08184153%2Fglobal-warming.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20visions%20and%20ideas%20for%20a%20global%20world%20order%3A%20This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20slogans%20of%20the%2060th%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20(MSC).%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20there%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20winners%20or%20losers%20among%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20globe.%20Instead%20each%20state%20should%20be%20able%20to%20benefit%20from%20international%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20the%20conference%20has%20invited%20representatives%20from%20countries%20in%20the%20so-called%20Global%20South%2C%20that%20is%20from%20countries%20in%20the%20southern%20hemisphere%20that%20are%20not%20Western%20industrialised%20nations.%20Whether%20from%20Asia%2C%20Africa%20or%20South%20America%2C%20there%20are%20guests%20in%20almost%20all%20panels%20making%20their%20perspectives%20heard.%20Could%20this%20be%20a%20first%20step%20toward%20a%20fairer%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20former%20Pakistani%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hina%20Rabbani%20Khar%2C%20more%20participation%20also%20means%20more%20opportunities.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20it%20used%20to%20be%2060-to-80-year-old%20white%20men%20talking%20hardcore%20security.%20We%E2%80%99re%20still%20talking%20hardcore%20security%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20it%20in%20a%20way%20which%20is%20slightly%20more%20diverse%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perspective%20from%20another%20region%20is%20crucial%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20formulating%20alternative%20strategies%2C%20Rabbani%20Khar%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20how%20Kenya%E2%80%99s%20former%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Raychelle%20Omamo%2C%20sees%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20the%20more%20voices%20you%20have%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20the%20more%20exciting%20the%20discussions%20are%20and%20the%20richer%20the%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20DW.%20Omamo%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Security%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20Advisory%20Council%2C%20which%20means%20she%20helps%20determine%20its%20direction.%20%E2%80%9CI%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20hearing%20perspectives%20from%20one%20side%20of%20the%20globe%20to%20the%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20also%20means%20climate%20and%20water%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20of%20the%20conference%20is%20on%20current%20conflicts%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Ukraine%20but%20also%20looks%20at%20how%20many%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20have%20turned%20away%20from%20the%20West.%20Climate%20change%20and%20migration%20as%20a%20result%20of%20environmental%20destruction%20are%20also%20a%20global%20threat.%20They%20are%20among%20the%20most%20pressing%20issues%20facing%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20people%20and%20are%20hitting%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20no%20longer%20means%20the%20same%20thing%20it%20did%20before%2C%20says%20Ambika%20Vishwanath.%20She%20is%20a%20co-founder%20and%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Kubernein%20Initiative%2C%20a%20geopolitical%20consulting%20firm%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20just%20about%20defence%20and%20military.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20about%20water%2C%20food%2C%20human%20health%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that%20is%20interconnected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanath%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20enough%20that%20more%20people%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20are%20represented%20at%20international%20conferences%20such%20as%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20though.%20She%20argues%20that%20other%20topics%20also%20need%20to%20be%20discussed%2C%20ones%20that%20are%20closer%20to%20ordinary%20people%E2%80%99s%20everyday%20lives.%20That%20includes%20things%20like%20climate%20change%20and%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20also%20why%20Vishwanath%20rejects%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CGlobal%20South%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20suggests%20that%20these%20issues%20don%E2%80%99t%20affect%20everyone.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20just%20say%20I%E2%80%99m%20having%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20discussion%20but%20%5Byou%20only%5D%20bring%20in%20more%20people%2C%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20have%20long%20term%20change%2C%20because%20what%20you%20are%20talking%20about%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20actually%20changed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%20Vishwanath%20has%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20conference%20for%20over%20ten%20years%20and%20she%20welcomes%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20group%20of%20participants%20is%20increasingly%20diverse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20rights%20versus%20security%20policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20accelerate%20cultural%20change%2C%20you%20have%20to%20create%20the%20space%20for%20it%20yourself%2C%20argues%20D%C3%BCzen%20Tekkal.%20She%20is%20a%20journalist%20and%20chairwoman%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20organisation%20Hawar.help%2C%20which%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20runs%20projects%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan.%20She%20is%20moderating%20a%20panel%20on%20sexual%20violence%20as%20a%20weapon%20of%20war%2C%20a%20topic%20that%20has%20received%20little%20attention%20at%20the%20security%20conference%20in%20the%20past.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20negative%20in%20seeing%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20represented%20by%20the%20Global%20South%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tekkal%20told%20DW.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20in%20the%20liberal%20West%20benefit%20from%20these%20experiences.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20is%20welcome.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%2C%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20conference%20do%20not%20invite%20representatives%20of%20repressive%20regimes.%20But%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20all%20participants%20have%20a%20clean%20slate.%20In%20addition%20to%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20government%20members%2C%20the%20controversial%20prime%20minister%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20is%20also%20attending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20upsets%20Saskia%20Bruysten%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20Yunus%20Social%20Business%20in%20Bangladesh%20alongside%20former%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winner%20Muhammad%20Yunus.%20Yunus%20was%20recently%20sentenced%20to%20prison%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20what%20human%20rights%20activists%20say%20was%20a%20politically%20motivated%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20that%20representatives%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20are%20represented%20here%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20shocking%20that%20someone%20like%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20is%20here%20on%20stage%20being%20applauded%20while%20she%20puts%20her%20only%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winner%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20in%20prison.%20Dialogue%20is%20important%20here%20on%20site%2C%20but%20we%20also%20have%20to%20address%20human%20rights%20issues%20and%20discuss%20them%20publicly%20and%20not%20just%20applaud%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bruysten%2C%20who%20sees%20herself%20representing%20Yunus%20in%20Munich%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETekkal%20argues%20that%20this%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20be%20about%20representation%20though.%20Human%20rights%20issues%20are%20not%20sufficiently%20integrated%20into%20the%20actual%20debates%20and%20the%20conference%20is%20still%20dominated%20by%20the%20military-industrial%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20we%20should%20start%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CExperience%20has%20shown%20that%20those%20who%20supply%20the%20weapons%20come%20from%20the%20Global%20North%2C%20but%20that%20those%20they%20target%20are%20from%20the%20Global%20South.%20And%20then%20there%20is%20always%20that%20question%3A%20Who%20is%20responsible%20for%20those%20killed%3F%20Those%20who%20shoot%20or%20those%20who%20deliver%20%5Bthe%20guns%5D%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmsc-2024-no-international-security-without-the-global-south%2Fa-68288812%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708407323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F08184153%2Fglobal-warming.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmsc-2024-no-international-security-without-the-global-south%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20is%20more%20diverse%20than%20ever%20before%20and%20there%20are%20more%20guests%20from%20the%20so-called%20Global%20South.%20The%20hope%20is%20they%20will%20bridge%20a%20growing%20rift.%20But%20how%20realistic%20is%20that%20really%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmsc-2024-no-international-security-without-the-global-south%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI's%20Arrest%20of%20Chanda%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20'Illegal'%2C%20an%20'Abuse%20of%20Power'%3A%20Bombay%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20of%20former%20ICICI%20Bank%20Managing%20Director%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Chanda%20Kochhar%20and%20her%20husband%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20was%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20power%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20routine%20arrest%20without%20application%20of%20mind%20and%20due%20regard%20to%20the%20law%20amounts%20to%20an%20abuse%20of%20power%20and%20does%20not%20satisfy%20the%20requirement%20of%20Section%2041A(3)%20CrPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Anuja%20Parbhudessai%20and%20N.R.%20Borkar%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fbombay-high-court%2Fbombay-high-court-chanda-kochhar-illegal-arrest-cbi-icici-bank-videocon-loan-fraud-case-249863%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20full%20order%20from%20February%206%20was%20made%20public%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20existence%20of%20circumstances%20or%20supportive%20material%20based%20on%20which%20the%20decision%20to%20arrest%20was%20taken%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20the%20arrest%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20contention%20that%20the%20couple%20was%20not%20cooperating%20with%20the%20probe%20also%20did%20not%20hold%20water%20with%20the%20court.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20right%20to%20silence%20emanates%20from%20Article%2020(3)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20which%20gives%20an%20accused%20the%20right%20against%20self-incrimination.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20exercise%20of%20the%20right%20to%20remain%20silent%20cannot%20be%20equated%20with%20non-cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20arrested%20on%20December%2023%2C%202022%2C%20in%20the%20Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20loan%20case.%20The%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20FIR%20in%20the%20case%20had%20been%20filed%20in%202019%20against%20the%20Kochhars%2C%20Venugopal%20Dhoot%20and%20others.%20The%20allegations%20were%20that%20ICICI%20Bank%20sanctioned%20six%20loans%20to%20Videocon%20Group%20companies%20after%20Chanda%20took%20charge%20between%202009%20and%202011.%20In%20return%2C%20Videocon%20invested%20in%20Nupower%2C%20a%20company%20linked%20to%20Deepak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kochhars%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20almost%20immediately%20after%20their%20arrest%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20material%20evidence%20against%20them.%20The%20were%20granted%20bail%20in%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20order%20on%20January%209%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708407083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcbis-arrest-of-chanda-deepak-kochhar-illegal-an-abuse-of-power-bombay-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CSuch%20routine%20arrest%20without%20application%20of%20mind%20and%20due%20regard%20to%20the%20law%20amounts%20to%20an%20abuse%20of%20power%20and%20does%20not%20satisfy%20the%20requirement%20of%20Section%2041A(3)%20CrPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcbis-arrest-of-chanda-deepak-kochhar-illegal-an-abuse-of-power-bom