20bastion%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20seat%20in%20Parliament%20three%20times%20in%20a%20row%20since%202004%20before%20defeating%20him%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsmriti-irani-holds-public-outreach-in-amethi-but-rahul-gandhi-gets-a-thumbs-up%2Fcid%2F2001645%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20underlining%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20connection%20with%20Amethi%E2%80%9D%20although%2C%20the%20paper%20wrote%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20clear%20whether%20Rahul%20would%20be%20contesting%20from%20here%20this%20time%20again.%20%E2%80%9CAmethi%20was%20known%20across%20the%20world%20because%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20(voters)%20have%20a%20strong%20bond%20with%20the%20family%20(Nehru-Gandhi).%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20loves%20you%20and%20you%20love%20him.%20You%20will%20never%20find%20such%20a%20good%20person%20anywhere%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAmar%20Ujala%3C%2Fem%3E%20notes%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20turned%20up%20in%20his%20former%20constituency%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20724%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amarujala.com%2Flucknow%2Frahul-s-nyaya-yatra-rahul-gandhi-reached-amethi-after-724-days-the-entire-city-gathered-in-the-one-and-a-ha-2024-02-19%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Centire%20town%20turned%20up%20to%20greet%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20jeep%20took%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20to%20traverse%20the%20route.%20Gandhi%20was%20aggressive%20and%20repeated%20his%20support%20for%20a%20caste%20census.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-face-off-as-rahul-yatra-reaches-lost-citadel-101708366626905.html%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20cites%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20ask%20in%20every%20meeting%2C%20what%20is%20the%20population%20of%20backwards%