to%20follow%20his%20passion.%20The%20teenager%20first%20wished%20to%20pursue%20engineering%2C%20for%20which%20he%20went%20to%20Kota%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20for%20coaching.%20As%20he%20attended%20classes%20for%20JEE%20coaching%2C%20his%20interest%20soon%20shifted%20to%20digital%20marketing%20and%20business%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20learning%20about%20SEO%20and%20marketing%20on%20YouTube.%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20digital%20marketing%20agency%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Class%209%20and%20earned%20about%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20The%20lockdown%20was%20also%20imposed%20during%20this%20time%20and%20I%20informed%20my%20father%20of%20my%20change%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20read%20stories%20of%20how%20parents%20force%20their%20children%20to%20pursue%20JEE%20and%20NEET%2C%20especially%20in%20Kota%2C%20Bablu%20Prajapati%20is%20an%20outlier.%20He%20asked%20his%20son%20to%20follow%20his%20passion%20and%20pursue%20education%20in%20the%20field%20of%20his%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20then%20completed%20his%20schooling%20through%20long%20distance%20education%20and%20moved%20to%20Indore%20where%20he%20is%20pursuing%20a%20BBA%20currently.%20His%20company%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20Adverse%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20all%20your%20digital%20marketing%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20are%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20future%3F%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340484%2Fmom-guilt-traveling-with-kid-moushmi-kapadia-vedansh-rigid-spine-muscular-dystrophy-rare-disease-trek-bike-travel-mother%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20to%20go%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20have%20my%20entire%20life%20ahead%20of%20me.%20First%2C%20I%20want%20my%20parents%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20mother%20and%20son%20are%20the%20perfect%20blend%20of%20passion%2C%20