n%20the%20branding%20and%20marketing%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20processing%20unit%20%E2%80%94%20all%20to%20help%20Kanthalloor%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20restore%20its%20generational%20millet%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20about%201%2C800%20kg%20of%20six%20types%20of%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20including%20finger%20millet%2C%20barnyard%20millet%2C%20little%20millet%2C%20foxtail%20millet%2C%20proso%20millet%2C%20and%20kodo%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20cultivated%20by%2025%20farmers%20on%2015%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village.%20This%20harvest%20has%20also%20been%20processed%20and%20packaged%2C%20and%20will%20be%20sold%20through%20the%20various%20channels.%20The%20farmers%20hail%20this%20initiative%20and%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20harbinger%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20human-centric%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20were%20earlier%20growing%20millets%20only%20for%20self-consumption%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454-150x100.jpeg%201