canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341793%2Fvalentines-day-love-stories-age-no-bar-senior-couples-remarriage-life-partners%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%203000%20Babies%20With%20Congenital%20Heart%20Diseases%20Have%20Been%20Saved%20By%20This%20Inspiring%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20Khatoon%20(26)%20remembers%2022%20February%2C%202023%2C%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20as%20she%20welcomed%20her%20first%20child%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20into%20the%20world.%20She%20was%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%20after%20eight%20days%20and%20was%20all%20set%20for%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20a%20new%20mother%20has%20to%20face.%20But%20two%20days%20after%20she%20went%20home%20with%20her%20bundle%20of%20joy%2C%20the%20concerned%20Kolkata%20resident%20started%20noticing%20alarming%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010-day-old%20baby%20was%20turning%20blue%20when%20he%20cried.%20They%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20a%20doctor%2C%20who%20diagnosed%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%20and%20advised%20the%20parents%20to%20take%20the%20baby%20to%20a%20bigger%20hospital.%20Wahida%20recounts%20that%20her%20son%20was%20then%20diagnosed%20with%20Congenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECHDs%20are%20present%20at%20birth%20and%20can%20affect%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%20and%20the%20way%20it%20works.%20They%20can%20affect%20how%20blood%20flows%20through%20the%20heart%20and%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body.%20CHDs%20can%20vary%20from%20mild%20(such%20as%20a%20small%20hole%20in%20the%20heart)%20to%20severe%20(such%20as%20missing%20or%20poorly%20formed%20parts%20of%20the%20heart).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30745481%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20nine%20out%20of%201%2C000%20babies%20have%20CHD.%20In%20India%2C%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20babies%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20this%20condition%20annually.%20One-fifth%20of%20these%20babies%20will%20likely%20need%20intervention%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20their%20life%2C%20due%20to%20a%20serious%20birth%20defect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%2C%20though%2C%20is%20twofold%2C%20as%20early%20and%20timely%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20this%20disease.%20But%20specialised%20care%20is%20lacking%20in%20most%20government%20institutions%2C%20which%20causes%20a%20financial%20constraint%20on%20parents%20with%20low%20incomes%2C%20like%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20found%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20timely%20intervention%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20d